<item>
            <title>[LU-5020] OST can be all mounted successfully in parallel mount scenario</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5020</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In parallel OST mount scenario, the MGC could be disconnected manually in &quot;lustre_start_mgc&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;furthermore, if the first mount failed, the corresponding OSS device will be destroyed asynchronously,&lt;br/&gt;
which will cause the following mount fail for it can&apos;t setup the OSS again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
